sentence: Is there a section of EECS 280 after 12 P.M. ?
sentence-with-vars: Is there a section of department0 number0 after 12 P.M. ?
sql: SELECT COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.END_TIME , COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.START_TIME , COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NUMBER , SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER , SEMESTERalias0.YEAR FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias0 , SEMESTER AS SEMESTERalias0 WHERE COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.START_TIME >= "12 : 00 : 00" AND COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID AND COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = 281 AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER = "WN" AND SEMESTERalias0.SEMESTER_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.SEMESTER AND SEMESTERalias0.YEAR = 2016 ;
